):

1. *Srcu* mi je prijalo njeno prisustvo. (My heart was delighted by her presence.)
2. Njeno lice je bilo srcem ispunjeno. (Her face was filled with heart.)
3. *Srcu* nikad nije bilo lakše. (Never was it easier for the heart.)
4. Pomirio se sa sudbinom i *srcu* mu je bilo lakše. (He reconciled with his fate and it was easier for his heart.)
5. Njena ljubav je mnogo vredela *srcu*. (Her love was very valuable to the heart.)